<p>Dear <%= username %></p>

<p>Your password has been reset. This might be at your own action or by an admin.</p>

<p>Click on the following link to set a new password:</p>

<strong><a href="<%= protocol + '://' + host + (port? `:${port}`: '') + '/#/resetPassword?uid=' + user.id +
    '&token=' + user.verificationToken %>"><%= protocol + '://' + host + (port? `:${port}`: '') + '/#/verify?uid=' + user.id +
        '&token=' + user.verificationToken %></a></strong>

<p>If you didn't reset your password, please get in contact with the LAYA administrator.</p>

<p>We wish you ongoing fun and success using LAYA!</p>
